    public class StaticPageVelocityViewController
extends VelocityViewController
    Special velocity view manager which shows static content which can be configured with StaticPageContentManager. The list of static page sections will be exposed under the name pageSections.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
